      "layout": "The page model is full-bleed, with content often spanning the entire viewport width, creating an immersive experience. The hero sections boldly present headlines or key visuals, sometimes centered over a background, maintaining a high-impact, direct communication. Section rhythm is driven by sharp transitions between content blocks, often defined by distinct background color changes or large text elements, creating a strong vertical flow without explicit dividers. Content arranges in layered or large-block compositions, prioritizing bold statements. While specific grid usage is not consistently evident across all content, there is a clear emphasis on large, singular visual statements. The navigation is a sticky top bar, minimal and discreet, often appearing as a floating overlay at the top of the viewport.",
